HEADWORD: Graf
<hw>Graf</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[G. Cf.
<er>-grave</er>.]</ety> <def>A German title of nobility, equivalent to
earl in English, or count in French. See <er>Earl</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
